snippet.title: Space Moth DX PC Gameplay - Arcade Mode
snippet.description:
Steam http://store.steampowered.com/app/425340/

Title: Space Moth DX
Genre: Action, Indie
Developer: 1CC Games 
Publisher: Black Shell Media 

Space Moth DX is the definitive edition of 1CC Games' intense arcade shoot 'em up, with a brand new DX Mode that will put even veteran bullet dodging skills to the test!

Beginners are catered for as well, with a re-balanced Arcade Mode that's just right for anyone looking to get started with bullet hell games. Face angry giant insects who want to stop you, Space Moth, from escaping earth and going to the moon. Show them who's boss and blast your way into space!
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
